Package org.citygml4j.jaxb.citygml.core._1

Class Summary
AbstractCityObjectType Type describing the abstract superclass of most CityGML features.
AbstractSiteType Type describing the abstract superclass for buildings, facilities, etc.
AddressPropertyType Denotes the relation of an _CityObject to its addresses.
AddressType Type for addresses.
CityModelType Type describing the "root" element of any city model file.
ExternalObjectReferenceType Java class for ExternalObjectReferenceType complex type.
ExternalReferenceType Type describing the reference to an corresponding object in an other information system, for example in the german cadastre ALKIS, the german topographic information system or ATKIS, or the OS MasterMap.
GeneralizationRelationType Denotes the relation of a _CityObject to its corresponding _CityObject in higher LOD, i.e. to the _CityObjects representing the same real world object in higher LOD.
ImplicitGeometryType Type for the implicit representation of a geometry.
ImplicitRepresentationPropertyType Denotes the relation of a _CityObject to its implicit geometry representation, which is a representation of a geometry by referencing a prototype and transforming it to its real position in space.
ObjectFactory This object contains factory methods for each Java content interface and Java element interface generated in the org.citygml4j.jaxb.citygml.core._1 package.
XalAddressPropertyType Denotes the relation of an Address feature to the xAL address element.
